snippet.title: Rock'n Roll gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Rock'n Roll, Dos PC game produced by Rainbow Arts in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/rock-n-roll/1165/
Rolling around mazes in this addictive and clever little puzzle game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
